{
  "stem": "26609.15",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They never had a fight, but he used to come.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Not too often he came home, and he had to leave for about a week or two.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Once he came home, and he told her that he is going to leave her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she was very much in love with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was a good looking man, but he was in the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he came home all-- another story I'll tell later-- all decorated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But later on, I know I felt that she told him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he never did anything against me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She told him in a way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "How, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I just suspected.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know for sure that when he told her that he's going to leave her, that he has an Ukrainian girl there, in Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It means Lwow was Ukraine once.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's now Ukraine, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he was promised a bigger farm there in [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Poland-- Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Eastern Poland is called Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So, she wanted to commit suicide when she heard that he's going to leave her for good-- with two children, of course.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, but I noticed something at night time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went the room-- the two children had their room just a door through both rooms near her, and I was a room further.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, during the night, I went in to see how the two, how they're covered or if they sleep.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, and as the door was open to their mother's room, I noticed something unusual, that she was sleeping and her arm hanging from bed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, straight away I went in and I noticed scattered on the floor tablets and a bottle standing nearby.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I understood that she wanted to commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
